1.1.8.name: wordpress/easy-contact-forms
1.1.8.description:
Easy Contact Forms sharply targeted at site visitors' needs.

Top 7 features:

  1. Visitor friendly contact forms.
  2. Easy to use form builder.
  3. Various field types and contact form field customization tools.
  4. Reasonable anti-spam protection and multiple data validation layers.
  5. Multiple contact form management.
  6. Easy to use contact management and entry management tool;
  7. Easy to use GUI.
